         <abstract>
            <p>A prayer to St George in several stanzas beginning with <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኦፍጡነ፡ ረድኤት፡</foreign>. The number of stanzas
               varies in the manuscripts. In several manuscripts, this prayer is followed immediately by a prayer to St Mary beginning with
               <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኦፈጣኒተ፡ ረድኤት፡</foreign>. </p>
         </abstract>
